OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FStarting with extensive and in
OL,6,Fplaces thick fog across the southeast,
OL,7,Fthis most clearing by mid-morning.
OL,8,FThen sunny, although the sunshine will
OL,9,Fbe often hazy. Becoming warm for
OL,10,Finland areas, whilst the coast remains
OL,11,Fcooler with light onshore winds
OL,12,Fdeveloping.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FLargely clear with a slight
OL,15,Ffrost, and perhaps patchy fog,
OL,16,Fdeveloping for some rural locations.
OL,17,FLater areas of low cloud are likely to
OL,18,Farrive, mainly across eastern areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
