OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,6,Fcloud will gradually disperse leaving
OL,7,Fsunny conditions before cloud
OL,8,Fincreases. Becoming warm inland again,
OL,9,Fexcept cooler across Kent and also for
OL,10,Fcoastal areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,13,Fbright or sunny spells and a chance of
OL,14,Fheavy showers, temperatures near
OL,15,Fnormal. Dry Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,16,Fbright or sunny spells, but windy on
OL,17,Fcoasts and turning cooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
